metadata.name: Tidal
metadata.description:
I love watching the stars parade overhead at the edge of the water, being at the ocean at night is something I've been familiar with from a very young age.

My earliest memory is of walking to the ocean with my dad during a storm. He called it a 'Midnight Mission' and it lives on in me as a small piece of magic and wonder I hope to pass on to my children some day.

I was two years old.
